            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 09:00:57 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1297803</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-16dba41 r-1adg3ll r-1b5gpbm r-a8ghvy" dir="ltr"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">由 2024 年 3 月 14 日至 31 日，旺角 T.O.P 商场将摇身一变成为全城瞩目的潮玩热点，万代食玩（BANDAI CANDY TOY）首次联手万代潮玩（BANDAI ART TOY，又称 BNESH 原创商品），举办「万代食玩 x 潮玩探索之旅」（Bandai Candy Toy x Art Toy Adventure）活动。活动以「冒险」为主题，将整座商场从 MTR/F 至 3/F 精心打造成一个超大型动漫乐园，各楼层设有特色打卡位及展品，让访客仿佛置身于一场惊喜连连的探索之旅，集观赏、购物与娱乐于一身，为动漫迷及市民带来前所未有的体验。</span></span></div><div dir="ltr"></div><div dir="ltr"><a title="IMG_5295" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54389641504/in/album-72177720324461119" data-flickr-embed="true"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54389641504_0c940d3eb4_h.jpg" alt="IMG_5295" width="1280" height="1600" /></a></div><div dir="ltr"><a title="DSC00024" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54389679158/in/album-72177720324461119" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54389679158_e8bdca2d24_h.jpg" alt="DSC00024" width="1600" height="1066" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><div dir="ltr"></div><h2 class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-rjixqe r-b88u0q" dir="ltr"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-b88u0q r-a8ghvy"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">活动亮点：1.8 米高「突击自由高达极」立像首度亮相海外</span></span></span></h2><div class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-rjixqe r-b88u0q" dir="ltr"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">活动的最大焦点莫过于海外首次亮相的全高 1.8 米的 FW GUNDAM CONVERGE「突击自由高达极」立像。这座以《机动战士高达 SEED FREEDOM》剧场版主角机为蓝本的立像，搭配充满科技感的设计地台，完美重现剧中机体的英姿，势必成为粉丝争相拍照的打卡热点。随著剧场版热潮持续升温，这款立像继去年「飞升自由高达」掀起话题后，再次为高达迷带来震撼视觉享受。</span></span></div><div dir="ltr"></div><div dir="ltr"><a title="DSC09904" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54388574427/in/album-72177720324461119" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54388574427_140cff5091_h.jpg" alt="DSC09904" width="1600" height="1066" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="DSC09838" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54389644639/in/album-72177720324461119" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54389644639_95ad7f2591_h.jpg" alt="DSC09838" width="1600" height="1066" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><h2 class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-rjixqe r-b88u0q" dir="ltr"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-b88u0q r-a8ghvy"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">期间限定店与人气商品</span></span></span></h2><div class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-rjixqe r-b88u0q" dir="ltr"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">活动期间，场内不仅展出多款人气及限定商品，更设有期间限定店，让访客可即时购买心仪的动漫周边，实现「睇得买得又玩得」的全方位体验。两款先行发售商品更将于活动期间抢先登场：</span></span></div><div dir="ltr"><h2 class="css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-rjixqe r-16dba41" dir="ltr"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-b88u0q r-a8ghvy"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">G FRAME FA 第 08MS 小队 SPECIAL SELECTION</s